### William's test site
Checking out GitHub to see if it will be a suitable place for Robert's website.
Need to find out storage maximum, and whether or not I can embed graphics from other storage sites.
```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
